MTG's%20fall%20from%20grace%20is%20more%20of%20a%20business%20story%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20cultural%20weight%20that%20let%20it%20achieve%20some%20meme-stock-like%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20about%20TMTG%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20good%20business.%20Its%20total%20revenue%20was%20%244.1%20million%20in%202023%2C%20which%20is%20a%20little%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-it-costs-to-open-a-chick-fil-a-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethan%20what%20a%20single%20McDonald's%20franchise%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20in%20a%20year%2C%20and%20it%20lost%20%2458%20million%20the%20same%20year.%20When%20the%20stock%20was%20near%20its%20highs%2C%20it%20was%20trading%20at%20something%20like%202%2C000%20times%20the%20company's%20annual%20revenue.%20That%20is%20a%20lot.%20Nvidia%2C%20the%20high-flying%20vanguard%20of%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20revolution%20and%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20stocks%20this%20year%2C%20is%20trading%20at%20about%2035%20times%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20required%20financial%20information%2C%20Trump's%20media%20outfit%20won't%20disclose%20central%20data%20points%20that%20would%20give%20a%20better%20picture%20of%20how%20well%20it%20is%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20likely%2C%20isn't%20%E2%80%94%20doing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-truth-social-users-disclose-financials-djt-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20my%20colleague%20Peter%20Kafka%20has%20pointed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20TMTG%20refuses%20to%20tell%20investors%20how%20many%20people%20are%20signing%20up%20for%20Truth%20Social%2C%20whether%20they're%20sticking%20with%20the%20platform%2C%20or%20what's%20happening%20in%20ad%20sales.%20In%20regulatory%20filings%2C%20the%20company%20says%20it%20%26quot%3Bbelieves%20that%20adhering%20to%20traditional%20key%20performance%20indicators%2C%20such%20as%20signups%2C%20average%20revenue%20per%20user%2C%20ad%20impressions%20and%20pricing%2C%20or%20active%20user%20accounts%20including%20monthly%20and%20daily%20active%20users%2C%20could%20potentially%20divert%20its%20focus%20from%20strategic%20evaluation%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20progress%20and%20growth%20of%20its%20business.%26quot%3B%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20doesn't%20think%20publicly%20disclosing%20how%20things%20are%20going%20will%20be%20good%20for%20its%20business%20prospects%2C%20which%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20tracks%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20the%20truth%20is%20probably%20bad.%20(To%20be%20clear%2C%20other%20publicly%20traded%20social-media%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20Reddit%20and%20Meta%2C%20do%20not%20keep%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20information%20under%20wraps.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20gloominess%20now%2C%20Trump's%20media%20company%20says%20it%20has%20bigger%20and%20brighter%20days%20ahead.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20TMTG%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftruth-social-to-launch-streaming-platform-1033252830%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20launch%20a%20streaming-TV%20platform%20where%20creators%20who%20can't%20find%20an%20audience%20for%20%26quot%3Bunjust%26quot%3B%20reasons%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20be%20cancelled.%26quot%3B%20The%20same%20day%2C%20its%20stock%20price%20fell%20by%2014%25%2C%20though%20the%20next%20day%20it%20bounced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETMTG%20isn't%20going%20under%20tomorrow.%20Its%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F5-things-you-might-not-know-about-devin-nunes-ceo-of-trump-media-technology-group-1031036814%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDevin%20Nunes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20yes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-dismisses-devin-nunes-cow-lawsuit-against-twitter-parody-accounts-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20Devin%20Nunes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20former%20US%20representative%20from%20California%20%E2%80%94%20has%20said%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fbusiness%2F4580023-trump-media-ceo-devin-nunes-says-truth-social-parent-company-is-well-positioned-in-response-to-criticism-over-profitability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillions%20of%20dollars%20in%20the%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20the%20boost%20from%20going%20public.%20He's%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Flivecoverage%2Fstock-market-today-earnings-04-19-2024%2Fcard%2Ftrump-media-shares-rise-ceo-asks-nasdaq-to-help-enforce-short-selling-rules-uyg9l2wIafI1mR25Lrv0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20push%20back%20against%20short%20sellers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20keep%20those%20betting%20against%20the%20company%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20for%20shareholders%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20fun%20roller-coaster%20ride.%20The%20stock%20is%20on%20a%20steady%20downward%20trajectory%2C%20and%20things%20aren't%20looking%20good.%20The%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fix%3Fdoc%3D%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F0001849635%2F000114036124019745%2Fny20026576x1_s1.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20filed%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20issue%20more%20shares%2C%20which%20would%20raise%20even%20more%20cash%20for%20operations%20but%20dilute%20the%20value%20for%20current%20shareholders.%20Trump%20himself%2C%20who%20owns%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20company's%20shares%2C%20is%20subject%20to%20a%20lockup%20period%20that%20prevents%20him%20from%20selling%20those%20shares%20for%20six%20months.%20This%20is%20pretty%20standard%20practice%20for%20SPACs%20to%20prevent%20pump-and-dumps.%20The%20board%20could%20speed%20that%20up%20and%20let%20him%20and%20other%20insiders%20sell%20earlier%2C%20which%20would%20give%20the%20former%20president%20a%20quick%20cash%20injection%20but%20almost%20certainly%20depress%20the%20stock's%20price%20more.%20Why%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20stock%20when%20even%20its%20namesake%20is%20giving%20it%20up%3F%20So%20DJT%20will%20likely%20circle%20the%20drain%20even%20faster%20once%20major%20shareholders%20are%20allowed%20to%20sell%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20really%20clear%20how%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20turn%20that%20around.%20Trump%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20some%20bigger%20fish%20to%20fry%2C%20like%20competing%20in%20an%20election%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-court-trial-falling-asleep-stay-awake-i-relate-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehanging%20out%20in%20court%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20TMTG's%20stock%20price%20has%20fallen%20isn't%20surprising.%20It's%20not%20a%20successful%20business%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20many%20people%20are%20ever%20going%20to%20want%20to%20hang%20out%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20let%20alone%20how%20many%20businesses%20would%20want%20to%20advertise%20there.%20The%20speed%20of%20the%20stock's%20plunge%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20shock.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20given%20that%20the%20gravity%20of%20reality%20would%20be%20such%20a%20strong%2C%20immediate%20force.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20the%20Trump%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20Group%20illusion%20seems%20to%20be%20coming%20undone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-djt-stock-price-crash-spac-lockup-sell-shares-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713777721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6620163449058e6693570354%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside