20Salary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20setback%20to%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20cancelled%20the%202016%20recruitment%20process%20for%20government-sponsored%20and%20aided%20schools.%20As%20many%20as%2025%2C753%20appointees%20are%20set%20to%20lose%20their%20jobs%20and%20return%20the%20salaries%20they%20have%20withdrawn%20since%20joining%20with%20a%2012%25%20interest%2C%20according%20to%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Debangsu%20Basak%20and%20Md%20Shabbar%20Rashidi%20said%20the%20school%20teachers%20recruited%20illegally%20after%20submitting%20blank%20OMR%20sheets%20must%20return%20their%20salaries%20within%20four%20weeks.%20District%20magistrates%20have%20been%20tasked%20with%20collecting%20the%20money%20from%20these%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20made%20an%20exception%20in%20its%20order%2C%20ensuring%20that%20one%20of%20the%20appointees%2C%20Soma%20Das%20who%20is%20undergoing%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20retains%20her%20job%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20formed%20on%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20direction%2C%20has%20also%20ordered%20the%20CBI%20to%20further%20probe%20the%20appointment%20process%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20three%20months.%20It%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission%20(WBSSC)%20to%20begin%20a%20fresh%20appointment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20challenge%20the%20order%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Several%20Trinamool%20leaders%2C%20including%20former%20education%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20and%20former%20officials%20are%20in%20jail%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20teacher%20recruitment%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Bengal%20targeted%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20over%20the%20court%20order%20and%20said%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20no.%202%20in%20the%20party%2C%20her%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20are%20set%20to%20face%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Court%20has%20cancelled%20about%2024%2C000%20SSC%20recruitments%20from%202016%2C%20CBI%20can%20take%20anyone%20into%20custody.%20A%20smile%20has%20appeared%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20worthy.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20nephew%20and%20his%20aunt%20will%20be%20defeated.%20%23TMCExposed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2023%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20State%20Level%20Selection%20Test-2016%20for%2024%2C640%20vacant%20posts%20while%2025%2C753%20appointment%20letters%20were%20issued%20against%20the%20vacancies%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawyer%20for%20some%20of%20the%20petitioners.%20This%20included%20posts%20of%20teachers%20of%20classes%209%2C%2010%2C%2011%20and%2012%20and%20group-C%20and%20D%20staffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20last%20year%20dismissed%20panels%20set%20up%20by%20the%20WBSCC%20in%202016%20and%20cancelled%20the%20appointment%20of%2036%2C000%20untrained%20primary%20teachers.%20The%20figure%20was%20later%20modified%20to%2032%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijit%20Ganguly%2C%20the%20judge%20who%20had%20also%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20in%20the%20case%2C%20resigned%20after%20several%20run-ins%20with%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20and%20is%20now%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%20after%20the%20initial%20judgment%2C%20another%20single-judge%20bench%20had%20paused%20it%20until%20further%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20November%20requested%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20to%20form%20a%20division%20bench%20to%20hear%20petitions%20and%20appeals%20in%20the%20recruitment%20case%20and%20gave%20six-month%20protection%20to%20those%20whose%20appointments%20were%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713774780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndt