0the%20CBI%20to%20undertake%20further%20investigation%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20appointment%20process%2C%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20in%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20directed%20the%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission%20to%20initiate%20a%20fresh%20appointment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2023%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20SLST-2016%20for%2024%2C640%20vacant%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2025%2C753%20appointment%20letters%20were%20issued%20against%20the%20vacancies%2C%20said%20Firdaus%20Shamim%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20some%20of%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20bench%20also%20rejected%20a%20prayer%20by%20some%20appellants%20for%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoments%20after%20the%20high%20court%20order%2C%20hundreds%20of%20school%20job%20aspirants%20waiting%20outside%20its%20premises%20rejoiced%2C%20as%20many%20broke%20into%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20this%20day.%20After%20years%20of%20struggle%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20justice%20has%20finally%20been%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20them%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20bench%2C%20formed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20high%20court%20on%20a%20direction%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20had%20extensively%20heard%20numerous%20petitions%20and%20appeals%20relating%20to%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20for%20appointment%20by%20the%20SSC%20in%20the%20categories%20of%20teachers%20of%20classes%209%2C%2010%2C%2011%20and%2012%20and%20group-C%20and%20D%20staffers%20through%20the%20SLST-2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20in%20the%20matters%20concluded%20on%20March%2020%20and%20judgment%20was%20reserved%20by%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20writ%20petitions%20by%20some%20candidates%20who%20appeared%20in%20SLST-2016%2C%20but%20did%20not%20get%20jobs%2C%20a%20single%20bench%20presided%20by%20Justice%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20ha