imesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109492957.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E'Queen%20of%20Tears'%20competes%20fiercely%20with%20'Crash%20Landing%20on%20You'%2C%20nearing%20a%20dramatic%20finale.%20As%20ratings%20soar%2C%20the%20series%20aims%20to%20make%20history%20by%20surpassing%20'Goblin'%20in%20the%20drama%20rating%20rankings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fqueen-of-tears-finale-week-achieves-highest-ratings-ever%2Farticleshow%2F109492957.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThreat%20To%20Life%20Not%20Higher%20Than...%26quot%3B%3A%20Minor%20Rape%20Survivor%20Allowed%20To%20Abort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20allowed%20a%2014-year-old%20rape%20survivor%20to%20terminate%20her%2030-week%20pregnancy%2C%20overturning%20an%20order%20by%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20The%20court%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20case%26quot%3B%20and%20allowed%20the%20abortion%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20hospital%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20law%20requires%20the%20court's%20permission%20to%20undergo%20abortion%20beyond%2024%20weeks%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20while%20undergoing%20abortion%20at%20this%20stage%20involves%20some%20risk%2C%20medical%20experts%20in%20this%20case%20have%20opined%20that%20the%20threat%20to%20life%20is%20not%20higher%20than%20the%20risk%20of%20full-term%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20allow%20the%20medical%20termination%20since%20she%20is%2014%20and%20it%20is%20a%20rape%20case%20and%20this%20is%20an%20exceptional%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager's%20mother%20had%20appealed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20re