ous%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Boele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20highlighted%20a%20seeming%20paradox%20in%20the%20market%3A%20High%20US%20interest%20rates%20would%20typically%20keep%20gold%20prices%20muted%2C%20but%20the%20opposite%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20these%20changes%20have%20occurred%20in%20the%20past%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20temporary%20in%20nature%20meaning%20that%20they%20could%20last%20around%20three%20to%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Boele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELofty%20gold%20prices%20now%20doesn't%20mean%20there's%20a%20supply%20crunch%2C%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20central%20bank%20buying%20is%20not%20justifying%20gold%20prices%20at%20current%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20Based%20on%20that%20assessment%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20keeping%20her%20forecast%20of%20%242%2C000%20per%20ounce%20of%20gold%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20below%20the%20current%20going%20rate%20around%20%242%2C400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-china-consumers-central-bank-pboc-economy-concerns-dedollarization-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662603de23b29110d30149c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-china-consumers-central-bank-pboc-economy-concerns-dedollarization-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20central%20bank%20has%20been%20on%20a%20buying%20spree%20for%2017%20straight%20months%20as%20it%20diversifies%20its%20holdings%20away%20from%20the%20US%20dollar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-china-consumers-central-bank-pboc-economy-concerns-dedollarization-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2