t%20of%20land%2C%20mulching%2C%20and%20drip%20irrigation.%20Weeding%20is%20also%20a%20common%20issue%20in%20growing%20strawberries%20on%20land.%20To%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20unwanted%20grass%2C%20we%20had%20to%20employ%20agricultural%20labourers.%20The%20labour%20charges%20alone%20would%20cost%20us%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20remove%20weeds%20from%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dheeraj%2C%20hydroponics%20farming%20seemed%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20went%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20undertake%20training%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDhakad%20Brothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20the%20hydroponics%20method%20of%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20hydroponics%20farming%2C%20you%20give%20nutrients%20to%20plants%20via%20water.%20A%20crop%20requires%2013%20kinds%20of%20nutrients%20including%20primary%20nutrients%20like%20nitrogen%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20and%20potassium%2C%20secondary%20nutrients%20like%20calcium%2C%20sulphur%2C%20and%20magnesium%2C%20and%20tertiary%20nutrients%20like%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20manganese%2C%20copper%2C%20boron%2C%20molybdenum%2C%20and%20chlorine.%20These%20elements%20act%20as%20an%20essential%20catalyst%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20knew%20the%20technique%20to%20give%20these%20nutrients%20via%20water%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20the%20ratio%20in%20which%20these%20elements%20were%20required%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20crop.%20The%20training%20helped%20me%20learn%20the%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Within%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%20Photo%3A%20Pixabay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5x%20more%20produce%20in%20small%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%2C%20Dheeraj%20established%20a%203%2C500%20sq%20ft%20hydroponics%20set-up%20on%20his%20farm.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20planted%209%2C000%20saplings%20of%20strawberries%20using%20coco%20peat%20as%20a%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20grow%20bags%20and%20filled%20them%20with%20cocopeat.%20In%20these%20grow%20bags%2C%20I%20connected%20four%20drippers%20for%20water%20supply%20and%20made%20four%20small%20holes%20for%20drainage.%20Next%2C%20I%20planted%20the%20saplings%20and%20supplied%20all%20the%20nutrients%20to%20the%20crop%20with%20water.%20With%20this%20method%2C%20I%20water%20the%20plant%20at%20a%20gap%20of%20a%20week%2C%20instead%20of%20running%20the%20water%20supply%2024%C3%977.%20Almost%2070%20percent%20of%20water%20gets%20absorbed%20in%20the%20media%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dheeraj%201.5%20months%20and%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20to%20build%20the%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20one-time%20investment%20that%20reduces%20the%20overall%20input%20costs%20after%20a%20certain%20period.%20For%20five%20years%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries%20and%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20period.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20method%20is%20far%20better%20than%20conventional%20farming.%20With%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20got%20five%20times%20more%20production%20in%20hydroponics%20compared%20to%20open-land%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20tasks%20farmers%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20while%20adopting%20this%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20need%20to%20monitor%20the%20hydroponics%20farm%20at%20least%20once%20every%20day.%20The%20strawberries%20are%20heavily%20attacked%20by%20pests%20and%20fungus.%20In%20land-based%20farming%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20spray%20chemical%20pesticides%20indiscriminately.%20But%20in%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20cut%20chemical%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Early%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20he%20prepared%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunique%20fungicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20curd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20litre%20of%20curd%2C%20add%2050%20grams%20of%20copper%20wires%20or%20a%20copper%20%3Cem%3Elota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spherical%20vessel).%20Keep%20the%20content%20for%20at%20least%2015%C2%A0%20days%20until%20the%20content%20becomes%20completely%20blue.%20Take%202%20ml%20of%20this%20mixture%20and%20dilute%20it%20in%201%20litre%20of%20water.%20Spray%20the%20diluted%20content%20on%20crops%20once%20every%20week%20throughout%20the%20season.%20This%20tackles%20fungi%20attack%20and%20gives%20a%20good%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20am%20extremely%20happy%20to%20reap%20benefits%20by%20adopting%20this%20new%20technique%2C%20initially%20I%20made%20some%20mistakes%20in%20getting%20good%20nutrients%20from%20the%20market.%20I%20got%20misled%20into%20buying%20nutrients%20from%20fraud%20companies.%20This%20delayed%20my%20production%20by%201.5%20months.%20But%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20next%20season%20from%20the%20same%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dheeraj%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20cultivating%20red%20and%20yellow%20varieties%20of%20capsicum%20on%20the%20hydroponics%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20example%2C%20Dheeraj%20advises%20other%20farmers%20to%20explore%20hydroponics%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20technique%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20any%20untutored%20farmer%20can%20reap%20handsome%20profits%20with%20hydroponics%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dheeraj%20Verma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-1-1713533722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Encouraged%20by%20the%20soil-less%20farming%20technique%20used%20in%20Israel%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Dheeraj%20Verma%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20strawberries%20using%20hydroponics.%20He%20earned%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20just%20two%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347819%2Fstrawberry-farming-in-uttar-pradesh-hydroponics-farm-in-barabanki-earns-farmer-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rakul%20redefines%20elegance%20in%20a%20pastel%20linen%20saree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109480098%2Cimgsize-38874.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Frakul-preet-singh-redefines-simplicity-and-elegance-