(in%20which%20people%20lacked%20the%20incentives%20or%20motivation).%20The%20latter%20may%20represent%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20society%20at%20large%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20former%20who%20have%20the%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Case%20For%20Democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insight%20is%20agnostic%20towards%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20political%20system.%20It%20may%20be%20presumed%20that%20in%20an%20authoritarian%20system%2C%20a%20government%20or%20leader%20is%20able%20to%20overrun%20vested%20interests%20more%20easily.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20government%20or%20leader%20could%20be%20totally%20captured%20by%20vested%20interests%20and%20the%20people%20have%20no%20recourse.%20It%20isn't%20surprising%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20there%20are%20some%20amazing%20success%20stories%20of%20what%20may%20be%20called%20'enlightened%20authoritarianism'%20(like%20South%20Korea%2C%20Singapore%2C%20China)%2C%20where%20governments%20were%20able%20to%20rise%20above%20vested%20interests.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20many%20more%20cases%20of%20destructive%20authoritarianism%20from%20every%20continent%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemocracy-is-spirit-that-supports-equality-dignity-pm-modi-to-us-congress-4145126%5C%22%3Ea%20democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20average%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20better%2C%20is%20because%20a%20government%2Fleader%2Fsystem%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20more%20responsive%20to%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people.%20But%20India's%20economic%20outcomes%20under%20a%20democratic%20system%20are%20a%20paradox.%20No%20collective%20population%20wills%20itself%20to%20be%20so%20poor%20for%20so%20long.%20India's%20per%20capita%20income%2010%20years%20ago%20was%20only%20%241%2C500.%20No%20collective%20population%20wills%20itself%20to%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20means%20of%20a%20better%20life%20-%20education%2C%20nutrition%2C%20healthcare.%20Despite%20the%20nationalisation%20of%20banks%20having%20been%20carried%20out%20in%201969%2C%20by%202014%2C%20only%20a%20minority%20of%20families%20had%20bank%20accounts.%20Despite%20an%20apparent%20welfare%20state%2C%20only%20a%20minority%20of%20recipients%20got%20a%20minority%20of%20their%20share%20of%20benefits%2C%20a%20fact%20admitted%20by%20India's%20late%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20when%20he%20was%20in%20office%2040%20years%20after%20independence.%20The%20state%20of%20basic%20infrastructure%2C%20whether%20roads%20or%20schools%20or%20hospitals%2C%20or%20toilets%2C%20was%20dismal.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Democracy%20Captured%20By%20Vested%20Interests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20India%20a%20democracy%3F%20Yes%2C%20it%20was.%20But%20it%20was%20a%20democracy%20captured%20by%20the%20interests%20of%20small%20groups.%20While%20the%20vast%20majority%20remained%20poor%2C%20there%20were%20groups%20that%20enjoyed%20much%20comfort%3A%20large%20farmers%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20businessmen%20protected%20by%20barriers%20to%20competition%2C%20public%20sector%20companies%20and%20employees%2C%20bureaucrats%2C%20middlemen%20who%20made%20a%20killing%20siphoning%20off%20funds%20meant%20for%20welfare%20or%20infrastructure%2C%20labour%20unions%2C%20political%20parties%20controlled%20by%20families%2C%20civil%20society%20outfits%20with%20%26quot%3Bpovertarian%26quot%3B%20outlooks%20-%20you%20get%20the%20drift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20occasion%2C%20a%20crisis%20spurred%20change%20for%20the%20wider%20good.%20The%20food%20crisis%20of%20the%20early%201960s%20led%20to%20the%20Green%20Revolution.%20The%20Balance%20of%20Payments%20crisis%20of%201991%20led%20to%20liberalisation.%20The%20fallout%20of%20the%20Nuclear%20Tests%20led%20to%20another%20round%20of%20liberalisation.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20did%20not%20change%20was%20the%20unresponsiveness%20of%20the%20state%20machinery.%20After%201991%2C%20the%20private%20sector%20drove%20India%20forward%20but%20often%20ran%20afoul%20of%20vested%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDriven%20By%20Aspiration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%202014%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment%20was%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20independence%2C%20a%20leader%20and%20his%20government%20had%20the%20conviction%20to%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20make%20it%20responsive%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20majority.%20The%20revamp%20of%20the%20welfare%20state%20with%20extensive%20use%20of%20technology%20has%20provided%20basic%20amenities%20(electricity%2C%20toilets%2C%20gas%20cylinders%2C%20piped%20drinking%20water)%20to%20every%20Indian.%20It%20has%20not%20made%20every%20Indian%20rich%20(per%20capita%20income%20is%20no%20longer%20low%20but%20a%20low%20middle%20income%20of%20%242%2C800)%2C%20but%20it%20has%20put%20them%20in%20a%20position%20to%20move%20upward.%20The%20building%20of%20world-class%20infrastructure%20(never%20the%20agenda%20of%20any%20small%20interest%20group)%20was%20also%20taken%20up%20with%20an%20efficiency%20unseen%20in%20the%20past.%20This%20is%20the%20base%20for%20attracting%20investment%20and%20creating%20jobs.%20The%20unique%20exercise%20of%20building%20a%20public%20digital%20infrastructure%20(Aadhar%2C%20UPI%2C%20the%20entire%20India%20digital%20stack)%20combined%20with%20cheap%20connectivity%20has%20provided%20people%20with%20opportunities%20to%20build%20livelihoods%20and%20improve%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%20And%20it%20has%20made%20the%20government%20more%20accountable.%20Big%20improvements%20in%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20have%20created%20an%20entire%20new%20generation%20of%20young%20entrepreneurs.%20Job-creating%20domestic%20manufacturing%20is%20receiving%20a%20long-overdue%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20recasting%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20average%20Indian%2C%20several%20vested%20interests%20have%20been%20disturbed%20or%20destroyed.%20Much%20sound%20and%20fury%20(always%20a%20comparative%20advantage)%20is%20to%20be%20expected.%20But%20it%20is%20this%20shift%20away%20from%20entrenched%20vested%20interests%2C%20pioneered%20by%20Modi%2C%20that%20is%20paving%20the%20way%20to%20meet%20the%20aspirations%20of%201.4%20billion%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Chief%20Economist%2C%20Vedanta)%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713764760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fh0a4rv5o_pmmodiani_640x480_13_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-modi-transformed-indias-governance-5495307%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%202014%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20contested%20vested%20interests%20and%20responded%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-modi-transformed-indias-governance-5495307%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-modi-transformed-indias-governance-5495307%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-modi-transformed-indias-governance-5495307%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20'Sound%20warning'%20that%20Quinton%E2%80%99s%20wife%20shared%20in%20CSK%20vs%20LSG%20match%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713764615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109491237%2Cimgsize-68290.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-tips%2Fexplained-what-is-sound-warning-on-apple-watch-that-quinton-de-kocks-wife-shared-during-chennai-super-kings-vs-lucknow-supergiants-ipl-match%2Farticleshow%2F109491243.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CSK's%20MS%20Dhoni's%20grand%20entrance%20at%20Ekana%20Cricket%20Stadium%20during%20IPL%20was%20electrifying.%20Sasha's%20Instagram%20story%20highlighted%20the%20Apple%20Watch's%20Noise%20app%20measuring%20sound%20levels.%20This%20feature%20is%20available%20on%20watchOS%206%20and%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%204.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-tips%2Fexplained-what-is-sound-warning-on-apple-watch-that-quinton-de-kocks-wife-shared-during-chennai-super-kings-vs-lucknow-supergiants-ipl-match%2Farticleshow%2F109491243.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWanted%20To%20Use%20Stronger%20Word%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gavaskar's%20Stern%20Message%20To%20BCCI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20season%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20has%20been%20a%20run%20fest%20so%20far.%20In%20just%2035%20matches%20so%20far%2C%20teams%20have%20breached%20the%20250-run%20mark%20five%20times%2C%20with%20SunRisers%20Hyderbad%20(SRH)%20achieving%20three%20of%20those%20totals.%20SRH%20have%20also%20broken%20the%20record%20for%20the%20biggest-ever%20IPL%20total%20not%20once%20but%20twice.%20Amid%20the%20run%20fest%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20former%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20warned%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%2C%20suggesting%20measures%20for%20protection%20of%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20has%20urged%20the%20BCCI%20to%20increase%20the%20length%20of%20the%20boundary%20by%20pushing%20the%20ropes%20and%20the%20advertisement%20board%20a%20little%20more%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20suggest%20any%20changes%20to%20a%20cricket%20bat%20because%20they%20are%20all%20within%20regulations%2C%20but%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20increase%20the%20size%20of%20the%20boundary%20at%20every%20ground.%20Look%20at%20this%20ground%20today%2C%20there%20is%20enough%20space%20to%20take%20it%20back%20a%20little%20more%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20metres.%20It%20can%20often%20prove%20to%20be%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20catch%20and%20a%20sixer.%20You%20can%20push%20that%20LED%20or%20advertisement%20boards%20even%20further%20so%20that%20the%20boundary%20rope%20can%20go%20back%20by%202-3%20metres%20and%20that%20will%20make%20a%20difference.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20bowlers%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20who%20will%20suffer%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20admitted%20that%20while%20power-hitting%20in%20IPL%20can%20be%20exciting%20at%20times%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20get%20boring%20eventually%2C%20highlighting%20the%20lack%20of%20contest%20between%20batters%20and%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20have%20been%20seeing%20in%20T20%20cricket%20over%20the%20last%20few%20days%20is%20that%20this%20is%20batting%20like%20the%20coach%20tells%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20'This%20is%20the%20last%20round%2C'%20and%20everybody%20starts%20swinging%20their%20bat%20around%20bang%2C%20bang%20whether%20they%20get%20out%20or%20not.%20It's%20enjoyable%20to%20a%20little%20extent%2C%20but%20after%20that%20it%20gets...not%20so%20exciting.%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20a%20stronger%20word%2C%20but%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713764520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ff89k0g2g_sunil-gavaskar_625x300_16_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwanted-to-use-stronger-word-but-sunil-gavaskars-stern-message-over-high-scoring-ipl-games-5491373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20run%20fest%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20former%20India%20captain%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20has%20warned%20the%20BCCI%2C%20suggesting%20measures%20for%20protection%20of%20bowlers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Singapore%2C%20Hong%20Kong%20Bans%20Sale%20Of%20MDH%2C%20Everest%20Spices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong%20has%20banned%20the%20sale%20of%20popular%20Indian%20spice%20brands%20MDH%20Pvt.%20and%20Everest%20Food%20Products%20Pvt.%20after%20the%20alleged%20detection%20of%20the%20carcinogenic%20pesticide%20ethylene%20oxide%20in%20several%20spice%20mixes.%20Singapore%20last%20week%20took%20similar%20action%20against%20Everest%2C%C2%A0alleging%20the%20presence%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20at%20levels%20surpassing%20permissible%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20For%20Food%20Safety%20of%20The%20Government%20of%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20Special%20Administrative%20Region%20announced%20on%20April%205%20that%20routine%20surveillance%20programs%20had%20uncovered%20the%20presence%20of%20ethylene%20oxide%20in%20three%20spice%20mixes%20from%20MDH%20Group%20-%20Madras%20Curry%20Powder%2C%20Sambhar%20Masala%20Powder%2C%20and%20Curry%20Powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CFS%20collected%20the%20above-mentioned%20samples%20from%20three%20retail%20outlets%20in%20Tsim%20Sha%20Tsui%20respectively%20for%20testing%20under%20its%20routine%20Food%20Surveillance%20Programme.%20The%20test%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20samples%20contained%20a%20pesticide%2C%20ethylene%20oxide.%20The%20CFS%20has%20informed%20the%20vendors%20concerned%20of%20the%20irregularities%20and%20instructed%20them%20to%20stop%20sale%20and%20remove%20from%20shelves%20the%20affected%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Fenglish%2Fpress%2F20240405_10919.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Everest%20Group's%20Fish%20Curry%20Masala%20was%20found%20to%20contain%20the%20pesticide.%20Ethylene%20oxide%2C%20classified%20as%20a%20Group%201%20carcinogen%20by%20the%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%2C%20poses%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20an%20elevated%20risk%20of%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20findings%2C%20both%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Singapore%20have%20taken%20action%20to%20protect%20public%20health.%20Singapore%2C%20in%20a%20parallel%20move%2C%20has%20also%20recalled%20Everest's%20products%20from%20its%20shelves%2C%20citing%20the%20presence%20of%20pesticides%20above%20safe%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20an%20Indian%20spice%20brand%20has%20faced%20action%20abroad.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20ordered%20a%20recall%20of%20Everest%20Food%20Products%20after%20they%20tested%20positive%20for%20Salmonella.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713764520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fbtqj1nk8_mdh-everest-masala-_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-singapore-hong-kong-bans-sale-of-mdh-everest-spices-5495187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hong%20Kong%20has%20banned%20the%20sale%20of%20popular%20Indian%20spice%20brands%20MDH%20Pvt.%20and%20Everest%20Food%20Products%20Pvt.%20after%20the%20alleged%20detection%20of%20the%20carcinogenic%20pesticide%20ethylene%20oxide%20in%20several%20spice%20mixes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-singapore-hong-kong-bans-sale-of-mdh-everest-spices-5495187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-singapore-hong-kong-bans-sale-of-mdh-everest-spices-5495187%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-singapore-hong-kong-bans-sale-of-mdh-everest-spices