d%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20FDA%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20manufacturers%20must%20ensure%20foods%20meet%20all%20applicable%20federal%20requirements%20from%20the%20FDA%20and%20USDA%20before%20entering%20the%20US%20market.%20So%20far%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20lab-grown%20meats%20have%20met%20these%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FDA%20continues%20to%20support%20innovation%20in%20food%20technologies%2C%20resulting%20in%20more%20choices%20for%20consumers%20in%20the%20marketplace%20while%20also%20prioritizing%20the%20safety%20of%20food%20produced%20through%20both%20new%20and%20traditional%20methods%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20have%20any%20questions%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20cell-cultivated%20food%20produced%20using%20the%20process%20evaluated%20by%20FDA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThey're%20'using%20cultivated%20meat%20as%20a%20cudgel%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20just%20silly'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20fledgling%20business%20of%20cultured%20meats%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flab-grown-meat-startup-solving-barrier-meat-without-slaughter-meatable-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20the%20need%20to%20slaughter%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20protein%2C%20diminish%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20factory%20farming%2C%20and%20disrupt%20the%20livestock%20industry%20as%20we%20know%20it%2C%20insiders%20working%20on%20bringing%20the%20lab-grown%20products%20to%20market%20say%20the%20innovations%20are%20anything%20but%20political.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erelative%20market%20share%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeef-companies-file-petition-against-lab-grown-meat-startups-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeat%20industry%20giants%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Cargill%20and%20Foster%20Farms%20and%20production%20capacity%20also%20remains%20far%20too%20small%20to%20represent%20any%20kind%20of%20threat%20to%20traditional%20livestock%20farming%2C%20industry%20insiders%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20lawmakers%20from%20targeting%20the%20industry%2C%20much%20to%20the%20dismay%20of%20those%20trying%20to%20bring%20their%20products%20to%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20past%20century%20of%20US%20prosperity%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20free%20market%20policies%2C%20and%20it's%20disappointing%20to%20see%20legislators%20move%20against%20what%20has%20driven%20the%20US%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20economy%20on%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20Peppou%2C%20CEO%20of%20Vow%2C%20which%20sells%20its%20cultivated%20meat%20product%20in%20Singapore%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BLet%20the%20market%20decide%20with%20their%20own%20wallets%2C%20not%20legislators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223396%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dish%20made%20with%20Good%20Meat's%20cultivated%20chicken%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20white%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661c574a1caec1275a6ffd26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222166%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20dish%20made%20with%20Good%20Meat's%20cultivated%20chicken%20is%20displayed%20at%20the%20Eat%20Just%20office%20in%20Alameda%2C%20California.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20authorized%20two%20California-based%20companies%2C%20Upside%20Foods%20and%20Good%20Meat%2C%20to%20sell%20chicken%20grown%20from%20cells%20in%20a%20lab.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20question%20there's%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20this%20right-left%20division%20using%20cultivated%20meat%20as%20a%20cudgel%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20just%20silly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tetrick%2C%20whose%20GOOD%20Meat%20has%20sold%20less%20than%2