ined%20and%20added%20to%20the%20team.%20Today.%20the%20team%20of%2025%20members%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20hurdle%20was%20cultivating%20a%20market%20for%20fonts.%20More%20people%2C%20including%20students%2C%20are%20now%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20quality%20fonts%2C%20recognising%20their%20impact%20on%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20communication%20and%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ITF%20office%20at%20Ahmedabad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-2048x2048.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EITF%20office%20at%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20of%20ITF%20fonts%20range%20from%20just%20Rs%202%2C500%