20villages.%20A%20homemaker%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335137%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-life-after-retirement-trekking-riding-travelling-biking-road-trips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E63-year-old%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20of%20responsibilities%E2%80%9D%20and%20wished%20to%20embark%20upon%20a%20journey%20of%20self-reliance%20by%20becoming%20an%20agriprenuer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20dinner%20table%20were%20two%20engineers%3A%20her%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20cold%20storage%20business.%20They%20were%20intrigued%20by%20her%20idea%20and%20immediately%20started%20looking%20at%20how%20to%20make%20her%20vision%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20in%20the%20following%20weeks%20and%20months%20that%20followed%20were%20no%20longer%20about%20the%20everyday%20mundanities%2C%20but%20rather%20about%20how%20saffron%20could%20be%20cultivated%20indoors%20and%20how%20they%20could%20achieve%20the%20necessary%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaffron%2C%20a%20highly%20valued%20spice%2C%20is%20exclusively%20grown%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20benefiting%20from%20its%20unique%20soil%20and%20weather%20conditions.%20Through%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20they%20replicated%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%20using%20IoT%20(Internet%20Of%20Things).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20by%20integrating%20technology%2C%20they%20planted%20the%20authentically%20sourced%20seeds%20in%20the%20cold%20storage%20chamber%20in%20August%202023%2C%20yielding%20their%20first%20harvest%20approximately%20three%20months%20later.%20Named%20%E2%80%98Shubhavni%20SmartFarms%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20commenced%20selling%20their%20first%20produce%20of%20two%20kilograms%20of%20saffron%20earlier%20this%20year.%20They%20have%20sold%20over%20Rs%208%20lakh%20worth%20of%20saffron%20and%20employed%2025%20women%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Shubha%20achieved%20this%20remarkable%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20business%20trip%20to%20Kashmir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20MA%20(Master%20of%20Arts)%20in%20Hindi%20from%20Shikohabad%2C%20Shubha%20got%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Mainpuri.%20She%20spent%20the%20next%2040%20years%20of%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20two%20children%3A%20a%20son%20and%20daughter%2C%20and%20later%20her%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubha%20started%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%20last%20year%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-min-1713440185-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShubha%20started%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%20last%20year%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20that%20she%20started%20looking%20for%20avenues%20to%20start%20a%20business.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20put%20my%20time%20and%20life%20to%20good%20use.%20Luck