20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20before%20she%20knocked%20on%20Kranti%E2%80%99s%20door%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverybody%20in%20Kranti%20has%20to%20do%20therapy.%20Therapy%20is%20the%20light%20in%20my%20life%3B%20it%20changed%20my%20entire%20worldview%20and%20enabled%20me%20to%20love%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sandhya%2C%20%E2%80%9CTherapy%20helps%20us%20to%20deal%20with%20our%20trauma%20so%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20carry%20it%20in%20our%20higher%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMental%20health%20is%20the%20biggest%20focus%20initially%2C%20shares%20Robin%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20years%20of%20being%20abused%2C%20girls%20start%20forming%20ideas%20in%20their%20head%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20capable%20of%20this%2C%20or%20I%20deserve%20to%20be%20treated%20like%20this.%20They%20feel%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20right%20to%20the%20good%20things.%20Watching%20these%20patterns%20change%20and%20overcoming%20these%20thoughts%20and%20misconceptions%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20classes%2C%20every%20Krantikari%20has%20to%20do%20two%20extracurricular%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20one%20physical%20and%20one%20artistic%20%E2%80%94%20choosing%20from%20karate%2C%20music%2C%20dance%2C%20photography%2C%20drums%20and%20many%20more.%20The%20theatre%20also%20forms%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20every%20girl%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20and%20they%20use%20this%20art%20form%20to%20share%20the%20story%20of%20sex%20workers%E2%80%99%20lives%20with%20people%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%E2%80%99s%20play%2C%20%E2%80%98Lal%20Batti%20Express%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20been%20performed%20across%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK.%20The%20girls%20also%20travel%20and%20conduct%20workshops%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%2016