l%20part%20for%20me%20has%20been%20seeing%20them%20grow%20as%20human%20beings.%20Everyone%20is%20working%20on%20studying%20either%20special%20needs%20education%2C%20gender%20studies%2C%20nursing%2C%20counselling%2C%20or%20psychology.%20They%20have%20all%20found%20their%20niche%20in%20social%20change.%20They%20have%20understood%20their%20purpose%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20support%20others%20through%20their%20journeys%20of%20healing%20and%20overcoming%20adversity%2C%20which%20makes%20me%20incredibly%20proud%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20social%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20like%20Sandhya%20are%20working%20with%20NGOs%20like%20Save%20the%20Child%20Foundation%2C%20while%20others%20like%20Shweta%20have%20returned%20to%20Kranti%20as%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20have%20things%20changed%20in%20terms%20of%20societal%20perception%3F%20Unfortunately%20not%2C%20rues%20Robin.%20The%20fact%20that%20they%20had%20to%20be%20evicted%20from%20nine%20houses%20is%20telling%20of%20the%20ground%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20tell%20people%20we%E2%80%99re%20running%20a%20home%20for%20orphans%2C%20they%20are%20fine%20with%20it.%20The%20moment%20they%20find%20out%20the%20truth%2C%20everything%20changes.%20All%20the%20neighbours%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20accepting%20suddenly%20become%20cold.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20run%20a%20home%20for%20orphans%20but%20not%20okay%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273849%2Fhero-smarajit-jana-durbar-collective-helps-kolkata-sex-worker-get-rights%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids%20of%20sex%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20societal%20stigma%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20most%20girls%20studying%20abroad%2C%20where%20there%20is%20less%20judgement%20and%20more%20acceptance.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20girls%20might%20study%20at%20the%20best%20universities%20and%20prove%20their%20worth%2C%20yet%20