%20only%20earn%20a%20livelihood%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20addressing%20the%20environmental%20challenges%20associated%20with%20non-biodegradable%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20changing%20times%2C%20Prashant%20realised%20that%20this%20training%20might%20not%20be%20viable%20after%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20keep%20changing%20with%20time.%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20might%20not%20be%20a%20very%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294290%2Fcouple-shares-personal-finance-tips-for-relationships-smart-money-management-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancially%20smart%20occupation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20future.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20started%20giving%20acupressure%20and%20massage%20training%20to%20visually%20impaired%20people.%20Massage%20is%20an%20excellent%20livelihood%20activity%20for%20visually%20challenged%20individuals%20because%20they%20possess%20sharp%20sensory%20abilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20methods%20are%20simple%20yet%20effective%2C%20allowing%20both%20less-educated%20and%20well-educated%20individuals%20to%20learn%20acupressure%20massage%20systematically%20and%20scientifically.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20course%2C%20students%20learn%20anatomy%2C%20physiology%2C%20and%20various%20massage%20techniques%20practically.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20become%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20of%20acupressure%20massage%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20individuals%20are%20trained%2C%20they%20can%20return%20to%20their%20native%20village%20and%20practise%20there%20or%20stay%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20earn%20at%20least%20Rs%20500%20per%20massage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20also%20helps%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20get%20married%20and%20start%20a%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20society%20looks%20at%20people%20with%20disabilit