opener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20their%20suburban%20Mumbai%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20moving%20to%20a%20smaller%20apartment%20to%20fund%20Hardika%E2%80%99s%20undergraduate%20education%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20supporting%20his%20own%20daughters%2C%20Hardika%E2%80%99s%20father%20also%20provided%20monetary%20aid%20to%20blind%20schools%20by%20sponsoring%20braille%20printers.%20The%20concept%20of%20giving%20back%20and%20its%20social%20impact%20was%20drilled%20into%20her.%20As%20an%20adult%2C%20when%20she%20found%20out%20about%20social%20entrepreneurship%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20she%20found%20the%20missing%20puzzle%20piece.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20after%2023%20years%20of%20being%20in%20the%20US%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202011%20to%20launch%20Kinara%20Capital.%20It%C2%A0%20provides%20unsecured%20loans%20to%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium-sized%20Enterprises%20(MSMEs)%20within%2024-48%20hours%20and%20has%20helped%20over%201%2C25%2C000%20business%20owners%20so%20far.%20Her%20vision%20was%20to%20provide%20capital%20to%20small%20business%20owners%20so%20that%20everyone%20could%20expand%20their%20ventures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20business%20has%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20women%2C%20be%20it%20in%20their%20personal%20team%2C%20where%20almost%2060%20percent%20top%20management%20are%20women%2C%20or%20through%20their%20%E2%80%98HerVikas%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20that%20provides%20discounted%20business%20loans%20for%20women-owned%20MSMEs%20to%20help%20them%20take%20their%20businesses%20to%20the%20next%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Hardika%20built%20this%20business%20which%20has%20disbursed%20over%20Rs%206%2C760%20crores%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeeds%20of%20social%20entrepreneurship%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20entering%20junior%20college%2C%20Hardika%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20too%20happy%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20could%20only%20choose%20one%20subject%20to%20major%20in.%20She%20was%20interested%20in%20multiple%20subjects%2C%20and%20wished%20for%20a%20course%20that%20would%20allow%20her%20that%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-2-1713159177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinara%20Capital%20targets%20the%20'missing%20middle'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-2-1713159177.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-2-1713159177-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-2-1713159177-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-2-1713159177-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-2-1713159177-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347266%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKinara%20Capital%20targets%20the%20%E2%80%98missing%20middle%E2%80%99%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20same%20time%2C%20her%20father%20who%20taught%20political%20science%2C%20would%20frequent%20the%20American%20library%20in%20Mumbai.%20He%20used%20to%20take%20his%20daughters%20there%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Here%2C%20Hardika%20came%20across%20the%20courses%20taught%20in%20American%20colleges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20discovered%20liberal%20arts%2C%20where%20you%20can%20study%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20subjects%20and%20still%20get%20a%20graduate%20degree.%20It%20was%20just%20what%20I%20wanted%20and%20after%20I%20learnt%20about%20it%2C%20it%20became%20my%20goal%20to%20pursue%20this%20course%20in%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hardika%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardika%E2%80%99s%20upbringing%20was%20non-traditional%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways.%20Her%20mother%20had%20been%20ostracised%20by%20her%20family%20for%20her%20choice%20of%20partner%20and%20faced%20many%20struggles%2C%20yet%20the%20family%20chose%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20live%20a%20life%20full%20of%20love%2C%20happiness%20and%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20unconventional%20upbringing%2C%20her%20parents%20allowed%20her%20and%20her%20sister%20to%20dream%20big%2C%20work%20during%20junior%20college%2C%20have%20different%20life%20experiences%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20go%20abroad%20for%20an%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20unheard%20of%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardika%20worked%20summers%20after%20finishing%20Class%2010%2C%20where%20her%20first%20job%20was%20working%20as%20a%20market%20researcher%20for%20shampoo%20fragrances.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20font%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20before%20going%20to%20college%2C%20I%20had%20to%20create%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%20on%20the%20computer.%20Since%20they%20wanted%20someone%20who%20could%20handle%20computers%20and%20had%20an%20artistic%20mind%2C%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20worked%20there%20for%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346774%2Fbengaluru-residents-saving-water-scarcity-rainwater-harvesting-recycle-greywayer-aerators-restrictors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%20resident.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20s