e%2C%20jaggery%2C%20garlic%2C%20and%20chillies%20paste.%20This%20mixture%20needs%20to%20be%20sprayed%20at%20a%20gap%20of%20two%20to%20three%20days.%20But%20when%20the%20damage%20on%20leaves%20is%20beyond%20control%2C%20we%20use%20permitted%20amounts%20of%20pesticides%20like%20chlorpyrifos.%20We%20only%20need%20to%20spray%20it%20once%20in%20a%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20four%20years%20to%20bear%20fruits%20in%20lemon%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Anand%20says%20he%20harvested%20400%20crates%20(or%20100%20tonnes)%20of%20lemons%2C%20which%20were%20sold%20between%20Rs%2040%20and%20Rs%2070%20in%20the%20local%20market.%20Interestingly%2C%20lemon%20farming%20also%20ensures%20a%20continuous%20inflow%20of%20income%20to%20Anand%20as%20lemons%20are%20in%20demand%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201.85%20lakh%2C%20today%2C%20Anand%20reaps%20profits%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%207%20lakh%20on%20his%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20More%20than%20the%20huge%20profits%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20finds%20contentment%20in%20leading%20a%20stress-free%20life%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20regret%20quitting%20my%20well-paying%20job.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20was%20a%20servant%20to%20a%20company%2C%20now%20I%20am%20a%20proud%20owner%20of%20a%20farm.%20I%20feel%20%3Cem%3Ethehrao%20%3C%2Fem%3E(composure)%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Anand%20Mishra.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713166036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-1-1712930139.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Observing%20the%20year-round%20demand%20for%20lemons%2C%20Anand%20Mishra%20switched%20from%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20like%20wheat%2C%20